data.description: ***Seller has decided to set an offer deadline for Friday 01/26/2024 at 6pm. Multiple offers received.  Thank you in advance for your offer...***Welcome to 456 Renfro Ct, a beautifully renovated home that strikes the perfect balance of comfort and style. This warm inviting residence features 3 bedrooms and two full baths, Meticulously renovated from top to bottom in 2022. Step into the heart of the home, where the open concept design seamlessly connects the living spaces. The main level features a spacious living area that opens to a beautiful gourmet kitchen, complete with black stainless steel appliances, a kitchen island for casual dining, and elegant quartz counters The fenced-in yard provides a private space for outdoor activities, and the rear deck is ideal for relaxing or entertaining. Descend to the fully finished basement, a versatile space offering endless possibilities. With a full bath, this area can serve as a guest suite, entertainment zone, or home office – the choice is yours. 456 Renfro Ct invites you to experience comfortable living with a touch of elegance. Don't miss out – schedule a viewing today to see how this home can be the perfect fit for your lifestyle!
